Company Profile
Our History
Maxnerva Technology Services Limited (stock code: 1037), formerly known as Daiwa Associate Holding Limited, was acquired by Hon Hai Precision Industry Co., Ltd (“Hon Hai”) along with other shareholders in October 2015 with headquarters in Hong Kong. Hon Hai is a Taiwan-listed global manufacturing services provider in the computer, communications and customer electronics industry. Maxnerva began implementing its technology innovation services to support China’s Industry 4.0 policy in transforming the country’s manufacturing segment.
With extensive experience in IT services and manufacturing, Maxnerva has become a leading end-to-end IT services and solutions provider.

