					Full Description



		Maxnerva Technology Services Limited, formerly Daiwa Associate Holdings Limited, is an investment holding company. The Company's segments include I.T. Integration and Solutions Services, and Electronic Products Manufacturing. The I.T. Integration and Solutions Services segment offers information technology (IT) products and provides project-based system integration services in the area of smart factory and smart office initiatives. The Electronic Products Manufacturing segment is focused on the professional production of telecommunication modules in mobile phone infrastructures. Its subsidiaries include Daiwa Nominees Limited, Grand Ditto Limited, Upright Ample Limited, Chiasso Inc. and Chinacorp Limited, which are engaged in investment holding; Daiwa Manufacturing Limited and (China Faith Electronics (Heyuan) Limited), which are engaged in manufacturing of electronic products, and Unity Electrical Industrial Limited, which is engaged in manufacturing of electric wires.
