Company Overview of Maxnerva Technology Services Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Maxnerva Technology Services Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures electronic products in Hong Kong and internationally. It operates through two segments, I.T. Integration and Solutions Services, and Electronic Products Manufacturing. The company engages in the production of telecommunication modules used in mobile phone infrastructures; and provision of system and network integration, information technology (I.T.) solutions development and implementation, and related maintenance services. It also manufactures electric wires. The company was formerly known as Daiwa Associate Holdings Limited and changed its name to Maxnerva Technology Services Limited in April 2016. Maxnerva T...
Maxnerva Technology Services Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures electronic products in Hong Kong and internationally. It operates through two segments, I.T. Integration and Solutions Services, and Electronic Products Manufacturing. The company engages in the production of telecommunication modules used in mobile phone infrastructures; and provision of system and network integration, information technology (I.T.) solutions development and implementation, and related maintenance services. It also manufactures electric wires. The company was formerly known as Daiwa Associate Holdings Limited and changed its name to Maxnerva Technology Services Limited in April 2016. Maxnerva Technology Services Limited was founded in 1979 and is based in Shatin, Hong Kong.
