Maxnerva Technology Services Limited Key Developments

Maxnerva Technology Services Limited Announces Audited Consolidated Cash Flow Results for the Full Year Ended March 31, 2017
Jul 28 17
Maxnerva Technology Services Limited announced audited consolidated cash flow results for the full year ended March 31, 2017. For the year, the company reported net cash generated from operating activities of HKD 44,840,000 against net cash used in operating activities of HKD 56,649,000 a year ago. Purchases of property, plant and equipment was HKD 27,731,000 against HKD 3,651,000 a year ago. Purchase of intangible assets was HKD 8,950,000 against HKD 1,833,000 a year ago.


Maxnerva Technology Services Limited Announces Change of Principal Place of Business
Jul 5 17
The board of directors of Maxnerva Technology Services Limited announced that the principal place of business of the company has been changed from Room 2138, 21/F, The Centre, 99 Queen's Road Central, Central, Hong Kong to Flat L-N, 15/F, Kings Wing Plaza 1, 3 On Kwan Street, Shatin with effect from 5 July 2017.


Maxnerva Technology Services Limited Recommends No Final Dividend for the Year Ended 31 March 2017
Jun 22 17
Maxnerva Technology Services Limited announced that the board does not recommend any payment of a final dividend in respect of the year ended 31 March 2017 compared to 23 cents per ordinary share paid a year ago.


