Company Description                    




                        Daiwa Associate Holdings Limited is principally engaged in the electronic components distribution, contract electronic manufacturing services, consumer electronics and electronic components manufacturing and distribution of personal computer products.  The Company operates in three segments: electronic components distribution, electronic products manufacturing and personal computer products distribution.  Daiwa Associate Holdings was incorporated in 1979 and is headquartered in Hong Kong.                     


